data.description: THIS IS YOUR CHANCE TO DEVELOP THIS 13.97 ACRES.  NOT IN CITY OF ATHENS, NO RESTRICTIONS.  Duplexes, quaint shops, Day care facility.  No Improvements on it.  Slightly rolling acres with 60% of native pasture on the back of the property and 45% woods on the front providing EXCELLENT entry with PRIVACY. This entire tract runs adjacent to the Athens Middle School, has 383' of frontage on Hwy 19.  Many possible uses, residential addition, commercial, country store, strip center, close to hospital, lots of potential!!  Check out the location and make a move for a great return on your investment.
